name: Tanks 'Easy Way Out,' Poster; Art Reproduction. Signed by Gotye! Very Limited.
description:
Limited stocks remain of this already limited edition! Signed by Gotye himself.

Limit, one (1) per customer.

Designed and illustrated to be used as a prop in Gotye's music video clip for 'Easy Way Out.' A high quality reproduction of this poster art was presented to Gotye (Wally De Backer) on the final day of shooting for the music video for 'Easy Way Out'.

The artwork depicts Gotye himself, in a poster designed to be reminiscent of a vintage cigarette advertisement for the fictional brand Tanks cigarettes. Fitting the theme of the music video. 

Strictly limited to 500 copies (Only 30 A3 copies signed by Gotye), you can own your own high quality art reproduction, just like the one presented to Gotye.

Each print is signed and numbered by the artist Jayden A Dowler.

This item is rare, strictly limited to 500 signed, A3 reproductions.

Only 30 of this A3 edition are signed by Gotye.

Specifications:

A3+, 100% cotton rag, archival quality ink. 

Allow up to 6-8 weeks for delivery, we appreciate your patience.
